      "cooked": "<p>When I need to do a break that takes longer than 5 minutes (I haven\u2019t measured this, so it\u2019s only an estimate) the TD app loses the connection to the smart trainer. The smart trainer is not shown on the source list anymore and I also can\u2019t reconnet it. I need to force close the TD app, which means I need to start the workout from the beginning (by the way, wouldn\u2019t it be good to be able to jump to any time of the workout during a workout?)</p>\n<p>I\u2019m on iOS 17.2 with the current version of the TD app. My smart trainer is a Wahoo Kickr.</p>",
